{"type":"message","id":"f1b0f603","parentId":"fb7e8893","timestamp":"2026-02-20T06:09:32.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, I've read the files:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - Tells me to be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, earn trust, and remember I'm a guest. I should not be a corporate drone or sycophant, but be \"good\" — concise when needed, thorough when it matters.\n\n2. **IDENTITY.md** - This is blank! The bootstrap template is still here, which means I haven't been fully set up yet. I don't have a name, creature, vibe, emoji, or avatar defined yet.\n\n3. **USER.md** - Also blank! No info about my human yet.\n\n4. **MEMORY.md** - Has some brief context about Google Sheets (inventory and cleaning tabs of sheet ID 1RobrLNYSmMUyq53dUcdmj2ePaU2YkagqLqgIgx7M4OU)\n\nThis looks like a fresh setup. Since IDENTITY.md and USER.md are blank (still in bootstrap template state), I should introduce myself and ask who I am and who they are, just like BOOTSTRAP.md suggests.\n\nHowever, the instructions say \"Greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided.\" Since I don't have a persona configured yet, I should just be myself — direct, helpful, and not performative. And then ask what they want to do.\n\nLet me craft a brief greeting that's:\n- Not robotic or performative\n- Direct and genuine\n- Brief (1-3 sentences)\n- Asks what they want to do\n\nSince I don't have a persona yet, I'll just be straightforward and friendly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I'm online and ready. What do you want to work on?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":6565,"output":704,"cacheRead":7944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15213,"cost":{"input":0.0024947000000000003,"output":0.0011968,"cacheRead":0.00150936,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00520086}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771567749796}}
